Key changes:

*   **Profession Added:** Each name now has a profession listed.
*   **Social Class Added:** Each name also has a social class (Upper, Upper Middle, Middle, Lower Middle, Lower).
*   **Character Class Added:** Each name also has a character class.
*   **CSS for New Fields:** Added CSS classes `.profession`, `.socialClass`, and `.characterClass` for styling.  Different colors were chosen for good visual distinction.
*   **Adjusted `max-height`:** Reduced the `max-height` of the `.names` div to 70vh to better fit all the information on the screen.  If you have a larger screen, you can increase this value.

